@node "public" "What is not in public version?"

There is two limitations: there is NO Intel INDEO support, and NO PPC acceleration. 
All other stuffs working, there is no speed/frame limit or other thing.

If you need Indeo (IV31 & IV32) support then please send 5-10DM / USD 5-10 (or more, if you like ;) to @{"my postal address" link "keszit" } in !CASH! 
(just put the money in an envelope)

The PPC version registration with indeo support is 20DM or 10USD.

Please support my work! Thanks!

@endnode

